ccess coverage isolated in the dedicated new file:\n  - `KerberosJdkProviderInnerSunJDKProviderTest.java`\n\nI did not run the Gradle test command locally, per workflow instructions.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09dfd6946d5cdeed0169f9fa99f77081a0a8fefbf3dbff6834\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2369, "output": 777, "cacheRead": 31232, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34378, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777990287040, "responseId": "resp_09dfd6946d5cdeed0169f9fa8fc95081a0846fd58bb072aae2"}}
